  <summary date="2024-01-11T13:51:49Z" status="Introduced in House">Ending Forced Arbitration of Race Discrimination Act of 2023 

This bill prohibits a predispute arbitration agreement from being valid or enforceable with respect to a case relating to a race discrimination dispute at the election of the person alleging the discrimination.</summary>
